OCaml-Ftp - OCaml functions for accessing files via ftp
=======================================================

Author: Samuel Mimram <samuel.mimram@ens-lyon.org>
Email: savonet-users@lists.sourceforge.net
Homepage: http://savonet.sourceforge.net/

Copyright (c) 2003-2004 the Savonet Team.


Disclamer / warning
===================
The implementation of the library is still very incomplete!
Patches are welcome :)


Dependencies
============
To build this library you need to have OCaml 3.07.


Installation
============
To compile the program type:

./configure
make

(you can set specific build options with the configure script, see
./configure --help) then, to install it, type as root:

make install


